hing in order to integrate, so who will be the point of contact from your site?\"},{\"Steve\":\"I will send you an email with the details he will nedd to setup the system. I am on leave till Thursday next week so any question in the meantime please use Support@talkative.uk I will advise the team that you may have questions about your trial\"},{\"Steve\":\"I\'ll also include that in the email to Jamie and yourself\"},{\"Customer\":\"thats great\"},{\"Customer\":\"we are in urgency actually.\"},{\"Customer\":\"We have to get this solution ASAP.\"},{\"Customer\":\"we will discuss price on Monday.\"},{\"Steve\":\"As I mentioned, I\'m on leave till Thursday next week. And Monday is a holiday in the UK.\"},{\"Customer\":\"no problrm on tuesday\"},{\"Customer\":\"problem*\"},{\"Steve\":\"We can discuss pricing once you have used the system a bit more\"},{\"Customer\":\"sounds good.\"},{\"Customer\":\"Have you sent email to Jamie?\"},{\"Steve\":\"I will draft you an email full of details now so you can get up and running.\"},{\"Customer\":\"ok waiting\"},{\"Customer\":\"Also I appreciate your prompt response Steve.\"},{\"Steve\":\"no problem, I\'m sure your developer will be fine. Do you know if you want to use Video as part of your trial?\"},{\"Customer\":\"Yes we want audio and video both.\"},{\"Steve\":\"ok\"},{\"Steve\":\"Audio is just video with video off FYI. We are deprecating our legacy voice calling option as it requires setting up SIP trunks and such.\"},{\"Customer\":\"also send detail procedure for magento 2, so he will not face any problem to integrate\"},{\"Steve\":\"We do not have specific integration with Magento. It\'s a simple Javascript snippet you add to the pages. Your developer will understand\"},{\"Customer\":\"sounds good.\"},{\"Customer\":\"Have you sent email?\"},{\"Steve\":\"2 minutes\"},{\"Customer\":\"ok\"},{\"Steve\":\"ok info sent over and invite email for trial has been sent\"},{\"Customer\":\"let me confirm with Jamie, received or not.\"},{\"Customer\":\"Yes he received and working on it, Thank you\\nIf I need any thing I will contact to support.\\nHave a good weekend  and holidays Steve.\"},{\"Steve\":\"ok, I\'m here till 5:30 pm UK time this evening. Let me know if he has any questions\"},{\"Steve\":\"Thanks you\"},{\"Steve\":\"We have a newer self service way of adding scripts to website that we can discuss next week. It\'s in Beta now but will available in a few weeks\"},{\"Steve\":\"Meanwhile use the exiting method I described here\"},{\"Customer\":\"he is working on it.\\nwhat is newer self service way? what will be the benefits?\"},{\"Steve\":\"You can manage and changes the design and options on the widget without having to make coding changes. It;s all managed in the Talkative interface so a no code - self service interface\"},{\"Steve\":\"will do once it\'s released\"},{\"Customer\":\"oh great we would love to have this.\\nplease inform this thing to Jamie as well.\"},{\"Customer\":\"I will also discuss this with him.\"},{\"Steve\":\"no problem\"},{\"Customer\":\"can I ask one thing?\"},{\"Steve\":\"sure\"},{\"Customer\":\"If  we take your chat and calling both solution, so let;s say a user come and click on call button now how our representative will get to know that there is a call?\"},{\"Customer\":\"any mobile app you have?\"},{\"Steve\":\"The user sign into the Talkative console and receives the interaction there.\"},{\"Steve\":\"There is a Mobile app for IOS and Android also but that has a lighter interface that only supports the core Chat with Translate and Video calling options\"},{\"Steve\":\"So things like customer history / Customer Journey / Cobrowse are not available via the App\"},{\"Customer\":\"so there is necessary to have app to call?\"},{\"Steve\":\"No, customer just has to have a WebRTC browser on either a desktop or Mobile device\"},{\"Steve\":\"Agent has a webrtc browser on Desktop or App on Mobile\"},{\"Steve\":\"WebRTC browsers are Chrome / Firefox / Edge or Safari\"},{\"Steve\":\"Agents should use Chrome or Firefox\"},{\"Customer\":\"ok its standard i think all must have these\"},{\"Customer\":\"I downloaded your mobile app\"},{\"Customer\":\"its not getting credentials which i created.\"},{\"Steve\":\"You have to have an account on Talkative . Jake will need to set you up an account\"},{\"Customer\":\"ok\"}]');
