ia lo del QR?\"},{\"Felix\":\"https://eu-engage-app.s3.eu-west-2.amazonaws.com/files/cf58fefa-5c8e-46cc-887a-4edd9dc61170\"},{\"Customer\":\"En cuanto tiempo puedo tener la implementación?\"},{\"Felix\":\"yes, it will include the QR code implementation. an implementation is 2-3 weeks normally\"},{\"Customer\":\"es posible en menos tiempo?\"},{\"Customer\":\"tenemos que lanzar un piloto lo mas pronto posible\"},{\"Felix\":\"it is possible\"},{\"Felix\":\"technically we can set you up today or tomorrow. but i will need to check on the QR code item\"},{\"Felix\":\"my email is fwinstone@talkative.uk i will check the QR code piece now and email you in 30 minutes\"},{\"Customer\":\"perfecto, muchas gracias Felix, quedo al pendiente\"},{\"Felix\":\"great\"},{\"Customer\":\"agradezco la atencion, bonito dia\"},{\"Customer\":\"Have a nice day\"}]');
